        "heading_cgTa8Q": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "color": "#000000",
            "text": "<p><strong>The Pluxy Epil Pro Essentials set is a thoughtful, all-in-one hair removal solution that senior women will actually use and love.</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "list_XffmV4": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "1. Gentle And Effective Hair Removal For Mature Skin",
            "text": "<p>My favorite, the Pluxy Epil Pro 3.0, featuring 17 hypoallergenic discs that <strong>remove even coarse facial hairs without irritation</strong>. It removes them instantly<strong> from the root</strong>, more <strong>gently </strong>than my old tweezers, but <strong>gets all the tiny hairs in seconds! </strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "list_dg6Fdw": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "2. Weeks of Smooth Skin, Not Days",
            "text": "<p>It’s so effective at <strong>catching all those tiny, hard-to-see hairs</strong> that one session leaves me <strong>smooth as a baby’s butt for up to 4 weeks</strong>. Not to mention, as it pulls from the root, the hair that does return is finer, softer and barely there. <strong>No more plucking ever again!</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "list_zTaACM": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "3. Soothing Aftercare For A Radiant, Youthful Glow",
            "text": "<p>The kit includes a massage treatment, which, when paired with your favorite moisturiser or cleanser, stimulates bloodflow for a <strong>plump, youthful-looking glow.</strong> It lifted my cheekbones and jowl, transformed my daily skincare routine and made taking care of myself from home effortless!</p>"
          }
        },
        "list_PxKXFA": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "4. Deep Cleanse for a Bright, Blemish-Free Complexion",
            "text": "<p>We all know that aging skin is darker, duller, and less vibrant. Well, the cleansing treatment gently buffs away dead skin cells and prevents ingrown hairs. It's a must-have for healthy, blemish-free skin between epilating sessions.</p>"
          }
        },
        "list_chkYbA": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "5. Safe, Gentle & Easy To Use",
            "text": "<p>The Precision Cover is pre-fitted onto the Epil Pro 3.0, making it easy to glide the device gently over contours, and target fine hairs on the upper lip, chin, or brows without any nicks or cuts. No more struggling with tricky angles or missed spots!</p>"
          }
        },
        "list_fRYfx9": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "6. Confidence on Your Terms",
            "text": "<p>With the Pluxy Essentials Bundle, she can enjoy professional-level hair removal results from the comfort of home. Each session leaves skin smooth and glowing for up to 4 weeks, anytime, any place. She’ll never rely on others to feel confident again.</p>"
          }
        },
        "list_XcLaRB": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "7. Dermatologist-Approved and Face-Safe for Mature Skin",
            "text": "<p>Pluxy's products are dermatologist-tested and free of harsh chemicals or irritating materials, making them safe and gentle for even the most sensitive skin types. You can gift with confidence, knowing she's getting the best.</p>"
          }
        },
        "list_BLwK7W": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "8. Incredible Value for an Effortless Self-Care System",
            "text": "<p>Purchased separately, the <strong>items in this set would cost over $200</strong>. But for a limited time, you can <strong>snag the Pluxy Epil Pro Essentials gift set for just $89.99</strong> - a savings of over $90. That’s six dermatologist-approved treatments for <strong>FREE</strong>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "list_NypkVi": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "9. Luxurious, Risk-Free Gifting Experience",
            "text": "<p>The set comes beautifully packaged, all ready to gift. Plus, with our 90-day guarantee, she can try it risk-free. If she's not thrilled, simply return it for a full refund - no questions asked.</p>"
          }
        },
        "list_jLmy3H": {
          "type": "list",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "10. A Gift That Keeps On Giving",
            "text": "<p>Sure you can gift her something she’ll pop on the shelf for till next year. The Pluxy Epil Pro Essentials set isn't just a one-time present - it's an investment in her self-care routine she’ll use everyday for years to come. Just imagine the joy as she looks in the mirror and loves what she sees</p>"
          }
        }
